---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CtaBanner from '../components/CtaBanner.astro';
import QuoteForm from '../components/QuoteForm.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<Layout title="Medicare Insurance Plans in North Carolina | Johnny Watts Agency" description="Compare Medicare Advantage, Supplement, and Part D plans with expert guidance from Johnny Watts Agency in Taylorsville, NC. Free consultations — call (828) 635-4200." jsonld={{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Service",
  "name": "Medicare Insurance",
  "provider": { "@type": "InsuranceAgency", "name": "Johnny Watts Agency" },
  "areaServed": { "@type": "State", "name": "North Carolina" },
  "description": "Expert Medicare guidance including Original Medicare, Medicare Advantage, Medicare Supplement, and Part D prescription drug plans.",
  "url": "https://johnnywattsagency.com/medicare/"
}}>

  <PageHero title="Medicare" subtitle="Navigating Your Medicare Options With Confidence" />

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="body-text-lg mb-6" data-aos="fade-up">
        Medicare is the federally provided healthcare insurance. Original Medicare provides for fundamental doctor and hospital costs. However, Original Medicare might not cover some expenses which can result in out-of-pocket expenses when getting treatment.
      </p>
      <p class="body-text-lg mb-6" data-aos="fade-up">
        To ensure that you will not be spending too much on these out-of-pocket expenses, you can get additional insurance coverage. We have extensive experience providing assistance and services to those seeking Medicare plans.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Medicare Parts -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-light">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="section-title text-center mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" style="font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 36px);">Understanding Medicare</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle text-center mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">Medicare has several parts, each covering different healthcare needs. Here's what you need to know.</p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <!-- Part A -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover-lift card-shadow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full mb-4 gradient-badge">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg font-heading">A</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title">Hospital Insurance</h3>
          <p class="body-text">Covers inpatient hospital stays, skilled nursing facility care, hospice care, and some home health care. Most people don't pay a premium for Part A.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Part B -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover-lift card-shadow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full mb-4 gradient-badge">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg font-heading">B</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title">Medical Insurance</h3>
          <p class="body-text">Covers doctor visits, outpatient care, preventive services, medical equipment, and some home health care. Part B has a monthly premium.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Part C -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover-lift card-shadow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full mb-4 gradient-badge">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg font-heading">C</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title">Medicare Advantage</h3>
          <p class="body-text">An all-in-one alternative to Original Medicare offered by private insurers. Includes Part A, Part B, and usually Part D. Often includes extra benefits like vision, dental, and hearing.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Part D -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover-lift card-shadow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full mb-4 gradient-badge">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg font-heading">D</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title">Prescription Drug Coverage</h3>
          <p class="body-text">Helps cover the cost of prescription medications. Available as a standalone plan or included in Medicare Advantage. Each plan has its own formulary of covered drugs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Medicare Supplement -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="section-title mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" style="font-size: clamp(22px, 4vw, 32px);">Medicare Supplement (Medigap)</h2>
      <p class="body-text-lg mb-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        Medicare Supplement Insurance, also known as Medigap, helps fill the "gaps" in Original Medicare. These policies can help pay for copayments, coinsurance, and deductibles that Original Medicare doesn't fully cover.
      </p>
      <p class="body-text-lg mb-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        With over 40 top insurance companies in our network, we compare rates and benefits to find the Medigap plan that fits your healthcare needs and budget. Our experienced agents walk you through every option so you can make a confident decision.
      </p>
      <p class="body-text-lg mb-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        Medigap policies are standardized by the federal government and labeled with letters (Plan A, Plan B, Plan F, Plan G, Plan N, and others). While benefits are standardized, premiums vary by carrier — which is why it pays to compare. We access rates from dozens of top-rated companies to find the best value for your situation.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Enrollment Periods -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-light">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="section-title text-center mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" style="font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 36px);">Important Enrollment Periods</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle text-center mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">Missing an enrollment window can mean paying penalties or waiting months for coverage. Here are the key dates to know.</p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover-lift card-shadow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full mb-4 gradient-badge">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6.75 3v2.25M17.25 3v2.25M3 18.75V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 012.25-2.25h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 7.5v11.25m-18 0A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75m-18 0v-7.5A2.25 2.25 0 015.25 9h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0121 11.25v7.5" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title">Initial Enrollment</h3>
          <p class="body-text">Your 7-month window begins 3 months before you turn 65, includes your birthday month, and ends 3 months after. This is the best time to enroll — no medical questions asked for Medigap.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover-lift card-shadow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full mb-4 gradient-badge">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.023 9.348h4.992v-.001M2.985 19.644v-4.992m0 0h4.992m-4.993 0l3.181 3.183a8.25 8.25 0 0013.803-3.7M4.031 9.865a8.25 8.25 0 0113.803-3.7l3.181 3.182" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title">Annual Enrollment</h3>
          <p class="body-text">October 15 through December 7 each year. During this period, you can switch Medicare Advantage plans, change Part D prescription drug plans, or return to Original Medicare.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover-lift card-shadow" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full mb-4 gradient-badge">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m9-.75a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-9 3.75h.008v.008H12v-.008z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title">Special Enrollment</h3>
          <p class="body-text">Qualifying life events — such as moving, losing employer coverage, or other special circumstances — may allow you to enroll or make changes outside of the standard enrollment periods.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Who's Eligible -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="section-title mb-4" data-aos="fade-up" style="font-size: clamp(22px, 4vw, 32px);">Who Is Eligible for Medicare?</h2>
      <p class="body-text-lg mb-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        Most people become eligible for Medicare at age 65. You may also qualify if you are under 65 and have received Social Security disability benefits for 24 months, or if you have been diagnosed with End-Stage Renal Disease (ESRD) or ALS (Lou Gehrig's disease).
      </p>
      <p class="body-text-lg mb-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        If you are still working past 65 and have employer coverage, you may choose to delay Medicare enrollment without penalty. However, the rules depend on the size of your employer, so it's important to get guidance before making that decision. Our team can help you understand your specific situation and avoid costly mistakes.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Work With Us -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-light">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="section-title mb-8 text-center" data-aos="fade-up" style="font-size: clamp(22px, 4vw, 32px);">Why Work With Johnny Watts Agency?</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1 gradient-badge">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="body-text text-dark"><strong class="font-medium">Over 40 years of experience</strong> helping families in North Carolina navigate Medicare. We know the local plans and the carriers that serve our community.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="150">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1 gradient-badge">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="body-text text-dark"><strong class="font-medium">We represent over 40 carriers</strong> — not just one company. That means we shop the market for you and recommend the plan that truly fits your needs, not the one that pays us the most.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1 gradient-badge">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="body-text text-dark"><strong class="font-medium">No cost to you.</strong> Our services are free. Insurance carriers pay us, so you get expert guidance without an extra bill.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="250">
          <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1 gradient-badge">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="body-text text-dark"><strong class="font-medium">Year-round support.</strong> We don't disappear after enrollment. If you have a billing question, need to file a claim, or want to review your plan at renewal, we're here.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-10" data-aos="fade-up">
        <a href="/medicare-quote/" class="hero-btn btn-shine inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3 bg-accent text-white text-base font-medium no-underline rounded-full">
          Get a Free Medicare Quote
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M190.5 66.9l22.2-22.2c9.4-9.4 24.6-9.4 33.9 0L441 239c9.4 9.4 9.4 24.6 0 33.9L246.6 467.3c-9.4 9.4-24.6 9.4-33.9 0l-22.2-22.2c-9.5-9.5-9.3-25 .4-34.3L311.4 296H24c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24v-32c0-13.3 10.7-24 24-24h287.4L190.9 101.2c-9.8-9.3-10-24.8-.4-34.3z"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Form -->
  <section class="pt-16 pb-16 bg-gray-light">
    <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-8" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2 class="font-heading font-light text-secondary" style="font-size: clamp(24px, 4vw, 36px);">Let's Have A Chat</h2>
      </div>
      <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <QuoteForm formName="medicare" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaBanner waveFill="#f3f4f6" />

</Layout>
